18:57.469 --> 19:00.097
- Rough day, sister.
How you holding up?

19:00.180 --> 19:01.265
{\an3}- I'm fine.

19:01.348 --> 19:03.183
{\an3}I think I handled it
really well.

19:03.267 --> 19:04.518
{\an3}Besides, she needs
to get married

19:04.601 --> 19:06.854
{\an3}so she can change
her last name.

19:06.937 --> 19:08.689
Virginia Ann Groves?

19:08.772 --> 19:10.315
Her monogram is VAG.

19:10.399 --> 19:12.150
